  "faq.q2":"What's the difference between Standard and Ultimate Edition?","faq.a2":"The Standard Edition ($79.99) contains the full game. The Ultimate Edition ($99.99) adds exclusive vehicles, weapons and outfits unlocked progressively through the story, with no decisive gameplay advantage.",
