  "price.r2sub":"Standard physical edition, no code","price.r2badge":"-25% vs official price","price.r2desc":"Several major retailers aligned on this price as soon as pre-orders opened. The most reliable tier below the official price.",
  "price.r3name":"PSN / Xbox gift card via Eneba or Instant Gaming","price.r3sub":"Digital version only","price.r3desc":"You buy a discounted gift card, top up your wallet, then pre-order at the official price on the store. Useful if you want the digital version.",
  "price.r4sub":"Physical edition","price.r4badge":"+ €20 store credit","price.r4desc":"No immediate discount, but store credit toward a future in-store purchase.",
