  "price.r6sub":"Direct digital purchase","price.r6desc":"No discount, but guaranteed pre-load from Nov 12 and zero risk of stock shortage.",
  "price.foot":"Comparison based on offers found at Amazon, Cdiscount, E.Leclerc, Auchan, Joybuy, Fnac, Micromania, Carrefour, Cultura, PlayStation Store and Xbox Store as of June 30, 2026. The official price remains 79.99 € (Standard) / 99.99 € (Ultimate), but several physical retailers undercut this price as soon as pre-orders opened — these offers are usually limited in time or stock. Always check the final price at checkout, promo code conditions, and seller reputation before buying any gift card on a third-party marketplace.",
